{"tid":47917,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前俄羅斯駐玻國外交官 頭部中槍倒斃莫斯科住所","createTime":"2016-12-20T16:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T17:13:50.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6693f79b94ae9daf2edffc99437382d26db49642","tid":47917,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T16:40:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161220/large/1482247854_ebb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161220%2Flarge%2F1482247854_ebb4.jpg&h=7932a869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 俄羅斯駐土耳其大使卡爾洛夫（Andrey Karlov）周一在安卡拉遭槍擊身亡，引來國際關注。就在卡爾洛夫死亡消息傳出後數小時，俄羅斯一名前外交官，亦被發現在莫斯科家中中彈身亡。<br />\n<br />\n現年56歲的波利希高夫（Petr Polshikov），周一被發現頭部中槍倒斃莫斯科住所，警方在屋內撿獲兩顆彈頭，並在浴室尋獲一把手槍，現場未有留下任何與行兇動機有關的證據。當地電視台報道，波利希高夫中槍時，其太太亦在家中，她未有受傷。<br />\n<br />\n報道指波利希高夫是俄國外交部專責拉丁美洲事務的資深官員，不過已經離職，未清楚他是否還有任職政府其他部門，他先前曾被派駐玻利維亞的俄國使館。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161220/56072725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161220%2F56072725&d=grcWnwNP2ffqGOZ2q3dXs6EBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=c6b6bb9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161220%2F56072725&h=8a269399\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161220/56072725</a>"},{"pid":"276b5c0bcf0a58ec34c06eb8e4aee796d6f488f6","tid":47917,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T16:47:59.000Z","msg":"#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" clas